{"tid":2001104,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【凡事Be Water】流水式悼念手足，有無得諗?","createTime":"2020-05-04T09:52:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-08T02:45:30.000Z","uid":134483,"like":50,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":49,"replies":[{"pid":"439c3878e03c2372cffa410cae2658294a69a1d7","tid":2001104,"uid":134483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T09:52:50.000Z","msg":"是咁的，每個月悼念手足既日子，即係721、831，每月8日(悼念周梓樂)，每月22日(悼念陳彥霖)，手足們已經會自發去指定地點搞悼念活動。不過班狗玻璃心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，佢地已經一早佈置好重防，一見群眾聚集就四圍咬人。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">「不受傷不被捕」</span></span><br />\n既然佢地有瘋狗症，我哋自然唔應該隨便畀佢哋咬。我哋都要進化，貫徹返「不受傷，不流血，不被捕」既理念，同時不死守，不陣地，流水式咁悼念。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">「前三後三」</span></span><br />\n咩意思？我哋由每個月既7.21(7.18-7.24)嘅前三日同後三日，都進行悼念活動，手足們行過太子站，就去獻花，或者將寫好嘅字條放低，做完就走。就睇下班狗係咪守足咁多日、清足咁多日！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不受傷，不流血，不被捕<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">Be water, my friend</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"a7bad62cb6062d85810ad35f720db667d4d7044a","tid":2001104,"uid":134483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T09:54:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4646c612a6fb2b588982976535ba0e0d7e25db85","tid":2001104,"uid":355363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T09:55:15.000Z","msg":"好想幫手推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a58eae7b873774ece24b819fcc06424cc03e331","tid":2001104,"uid":326261,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T09:55:56.000Z","msg":"終於都見到啲有用嘅嘢啦"},{"pid":"425808d5f8ccb847894afc55bc7d45a45a1386be","tid":2001104,"uid":326261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T09:56:06.000Z","msg":"Up"},{"pid":"b84c8fb9091193d15775c13ca610f038d85f007f","tid":2001104,"uid":337761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T09:56:07.000Z","msg":"唔好意思借少少位<br />\n<br />\n疫情將快過，全球局勢大洗牌，明年八月後打Twitter戰線可能犯法<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1998541\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1998541</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n－－－<br />\n入去 <a href=\"http://t.me/TwitterHelpBot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTwitterHelpBot&d=QLsQNhMpkN58D9M0TNJg1vsPRfgRtgRFNgQ5kFpanIU%3D&h=1739f6ef\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/TwitterHelpBot</a> 撳 /task 拎任務<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">Retweet + Like + Reply</span></span><br />\n國際戰線長期好缺人，大家快啲去幫手！<br />\n光復香港，撳幾個掣都做唔到？<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">Task 2 目前缺人，入 <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">/task2</span></span> 幫下手！</span><br />\n</span></strong><br />\n光復香港，你我有責<br />\n國際戰線，多你一個好多"},{"pid":"6af4e8b757d85b6cfca7787663c2af37b618d4ab","tid":2001104,"uid":326261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T09:56:20.000Z","msg":"Up"},{"pid":"205f0d48834996de39a63843c8ccfdd8f8c23414","tid":2001104,"uid":197716,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T09:57:17.000Z","msg":"好post 好耐冇be water<br />\nBe water意思係食變化"},{"pid":"b6b64ed33e9fecb11a5395657291190549cebe0b","tid":2001104,"uid":197716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T09:57:51.000Z","msg":"唔知上唔上到熱門"},{"pid":"253f0c72067a2cd7972c7678c535dc49ef5553d4","tid":2001104,"uid":134483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T09:58:38.000Z","msg":"推到熱門"},{"pid":"e39f6321a3be17d3427de834eda723140397760a","tid":2001104,"uid":134483,"like":0,"dislike":0