ji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n悼念要繼續，但我地唔能夠再承受失去手足嘅結果<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6155b8fef668617547c618c5fa41f8aac043ee7f","tid":2001104,"uid":155926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d8a5a3798ddea4185e85e02e0e39f480988b875c","tid":2001104,"uid":219277,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T04:15:04.000Z","msg":"太子岩岩果次都算係流水式<br />\n不過時間無你講嘅咁多日"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T04:39:28.000Z","msg":"目的兩個：<br />\n1）睇下對家反應<br />\n2）減少被捕，保護手足"},{"pid":"08fab051e844a96b0ff976b6846f53162ba7e841","tid":2001104,"uid":155926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T04:39:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0cd441bc25e81a810f02c2530b062a4e58cbbff0","tid":2001104,"uid":305080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T04:40:30.000Z","msg":"feasible, pushhh"},{"pid":"b7558b8042f996fb372f95c329f7dd8c4e94524a","tid":2001104,"uid":310461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"439c3878e03c2372cffa410cae2658294a69a1d7","tid":2001104,"uid":134483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T09:52:50.000Z","msg":"是咁的，每個月悼念手足既日子，即係721、831，每月8日(悼念周梓樂)，每月22日(悼念陳彥霖)，手足們已經會自發去指定地點搞悼念活動。不過班狗玻璃心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，佢地已經一早佈置好重防，一見群眾聚集就四圍咬人。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">「不受傷不被捕」</span></span><br />\n既然佢地有瘋狗症，我哋自然唔應該隨便畀佢哋咬。我哋都要進化，貫徹返「不受傷，不流血，不被捕」既理念，同時不死守，不陣地，流水式咁悼念。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">「前三後三」</span></span><br />\n咩意思？我哋由每個月既7.21(7.18-7.24)嘅前三日同後三日，都進行悼念活動，手足們行過太子站，就去獻花，或者將寫好嘅字條放低，做完就走。就睇下班狗係咪守足咁多日、清足咁多日！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不受傷，不流血，不被捕<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">Be water, my friend</span></strong></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T04:46:42.000Z","msg":"Creative.."},{"pid":"17e66f73658f10eade1d75efe3d72fcb6e7a554e","tid":2001104,"uid":155926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T06:09:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1dcd0a603db3b19398e7d1d0b115066879578801","tid":2001104,"uid":78892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T06:12:28.000Z","msg":"推,等班狗罰企多幾日又打唔到人,番去打老婆打仔,又有核彈可以推<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99f3cb34efb25c7ee6186d3c1878f19107213170","tid":2001104,"uid":155926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T06:13:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d4622884f641e84e7ddc5cb4ea9fad65ef97923","tid":2001104,"uid":155926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T16:17:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/fa